          "context": "Tom: Hey Maria, I keep getting `NaN` when I add my form values.\n\nMaria: Form inputs are strings. `\"2\" + 2` is `\"22\"`, but `\"2\" - 2` is `0`. Convert with `Number()` first.\n\nTom: Ah, so `Number(\"2\") + 2` gives `4`. Thanks!",
